{"tid":1024131,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想追內向（？）嘅女仔","createTime":"2019-02-16T10:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T16:30:06.000Z","uid":203489,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9a4e8f1d636dee489df00a0909957525cdcb1061","tid":1024131,"uid":203489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"啱啱識咗個同學對佢有興趣唔知可以點入手<br />\n正常對答就幾開朗，不過見佢whatsapp 好少online，ig 又唔過50人follow 唔知可以點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cf7759a33e9e209a872fbdf7a2abffacced357","tid":1024131,"uid":224107,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真答：投其所好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127e4715d5886b377f8c9240f893730bb791838b","tid":1024131,"uid":130586,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"慢慢嚟<br />\n逐步進入佢生活 令佢覺得同你相處係舒服嘅<br />\n做朋友先 乜都傾下 <br />\n樓上話投其所好都好重要 咁先有話題<br />\n突然一副想追人嘅樣會嚇親佢<br />\n如果真係內向又同你唔熟 <br />\n你副進擊樣會令佢覺得你入侵私入領土"},{"pid":"8e85f3703099830904a7281d3a18e77be1889b4d","tid":1024131,"uid":60866,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:02:21.000Z","msg":"同埋記住要有耐性啊<br />\n多數內向嘅女仔都好被動<br />\n就算內心有好多感受都會收收埋埋<br />\n所以就算你做好多嘢 好多時都會得唔到回應<br />\n但如果真係鍾意就唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e57adfe7f06eba84f0e6c46c011e6f9238711d","tid":1024131,"uid":6378,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"正評支持下"},{"pid":"2da024a0d896d8aa7e265a83f1c7d122f5e7277c","tid":1024131,"uid":220068,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:25:18.000Z","msg":"返學應該有好多時間相處既<br />\n佢應該乖乖女黎 用多啲時間面對面相處先<br />\n一齊做吓功課 又可以有機會落堂食吓飯<br />\n了解多啲對方有咗共同話題<br />\n熟咗先再傾多啲wtsapp<br />\n如果宜家未係好熟 走去傾咁多wtsapp就冇咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7f794c015dc0f5cf8f77db593102e48a068826","tid":1024131,"uid":203489,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996d84bc088db40983b82bcbd9b2875fe56bc6a2","tid":1024131,"uid":67765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f7f794c015dc0f5cf8f77db593102e48a068826","tid":1024131,"uid":203489,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57dca856437cc2a20df19b06ed1b11d43778449","tid":1024131,"uid":203489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"996d84bc088db40983b82bcbd9b2875fe56bc6a2","tid":1024131,"uid":67765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f7f794c015dc0f5cf8f77db593102e48a068826","tid":1024131,"uid":203489,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2383b4654f80a6bbdb07d752cd8cdb85e1b5053d","tid":1024131,"uid":67765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f57dca856437cc2a20df19b06ed1b11d43778449","tid":1024131,"uid":203489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"996d84bc088db40983b82bcbd9b2875fe56bc6a2","tid":1024131,"uid":67765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f7f794c015dc0f5cf8f77db593102e48a068826","tid":1024131,"uid":203489,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj